":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":7425,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/02\/amnesty-mecca-liberated\/","url_meta":{"origin":6594,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Mercy: General amnesty the day Mecca is liberated","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 2, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: In the year of Mecca's liberation, Al-Abbas ibn Abdul Muttalib came to the Messenger of Allah, peace be upon him, with Abu Sufyan ibn Harb and he embraced Islam. Al-Abbas said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, Abu Sufyan is a proud man, so give him something.\u201d The Prophet\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":8258,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/15\/every-treaty-justice-affirmed\/","url_meta":{"origin":6594,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Pacts: Every treaty of justice before Islam affirmed","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 15, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cEvery just pact from the time of ignorance is not increased by Islam but in strength and affirmation.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 2909 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Ahmad Shakir Zuhrah said, \u201cIt is a just pact such as the Hilf\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":9887,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/11\/22\/fath-makkah-day-rahmah\/","url_meta":{"origin":6594,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Fath: Liberation of Mecca is a day of mercy","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 22, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Asakir reported: When Sa\u2019d passed by Abu Sufyan with the banner of the Prophet on the day Mecca was liberated, he announced, \u201cO Abu Sufyan! Today is a day of slaughter! Today the unlawful will be lawful! Today Allah will disgrace the Quraish!\u201d So the Messenger of Allah, peace\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":6290,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/12\/prophet-loves-makkah\/","url_meta":{"origin":6594,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Makkah: The Prophet loves his hometown of Mecca","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 12, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn 'Adi reported: I saw the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, while he was standing near Mecca and saying, \u201cBy Allah, you are the best and most beloved land to Allah. Had I not been driven away from you, I would not have left you.\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":7321,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/30\/every-prophet-shepherd\/","url_meta":{"origin":6594,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Anbiya: All of the prophets were good shepherds","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 30, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cAllah did not send any prophet but that he cared for sheep.\u201d The companions asked, \u201cAnd you as well?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cYes. I was a shepherd with a modest wage on behalf of the people of Mecca.\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/6594","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=6594"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/6594\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=6594"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=6594"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=6594"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}